methods.name: getLanguage
methods.description: Returns the language last reported by the player as their local language. Defaults to en_us if the value is unknown.

methods.name: setTabListHeader
methods.description: Set the tab list header while preserving the footer.

methods.name: setTabListFooter
methods.description: Set the tab list footer while preserving the header.

methods.name: setTabListHeaderFooter
methods.description: Set the tab list header and footer at once.

methods.name: refreshTabListName
methods.description: Force the name displayed in the tab list to refresh, by firing PlayerEvent.TabListNameFormat .
